Package: ggsaveR
Title: A Wrapper for 'ggplot2::ggsave' with Extra Features
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Anders Hagen", "Jarmund", , "anders.h.jarmund@ntnu.no", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Extends the functionality of 'ggplot2::ggsave()' to allow for 
    saving plots to multiple formats at once, embedding plot data within PNG 
    files for reproducibility, and automatically generating unique filenames 
    to prevent overwriting existing files.
